19. `workspaceAndWarpAvailable` short-circuits to false WITHOUT calling fetch when flag is off (assert fetchImpl never called)
20. `workspaceAndWarpAvailable` calls fetch and returns true when flag on + endpoint 200
21. `workspaceAndWarpAvailable` calls fetch and returns false when flag on + endpoint 404
22. `workspaceAndWarpAvailable` calls fetch and returns false when flag on + fetch throws

Use vi.stubEnv / vi.unstubAllEnvs in setup/teardown to manipulate process.env per test case.

